{"tid":1333853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［炎炎消防隊］買個滅火筒","createTime":"2019-07-20T01:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T03:11:51.000Z","uid":186,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"257d53328b7e322efa379f5093c8f24ad99e921a","tid":1333853,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://maple.bilibili.to/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/316570.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaple.bilibili.to%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F316570.jpg&h=84c5f490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHX4scj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHX4scj.png&h=97376121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=c971c355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>地產】新聞時不時就報導，有市民使用抽濕機、電風扇、甚至電熱氈不當，或者日久失修，引致電線短路、機件過熱，終於發生火警。有時易燃化學清潔噴劑或者殺蟲水太接近廚房爐火，亦會引發小火。<br />\n<br />\n所以你就諗，不如買個滅火筒返蝸居看門口，一旦不幸屋內發生小火，都可以即時撲滅。<br />\n<br />\n市面上買到嘅手提式滅火筒，常見有四種類型：<br />\n<br />\n水劑型：射程有六米遠；適合撲滅由紙張、布塊、木材、塑膠、雜物等引起嘅火警。<br />\n<br />\n泡劑型：射程有四至六米；除咗適合撲滅上述嘅普通火種外，亦啱撲熄由火水、電油、酒精等嘅易燃液體或者油類引起嘅火警。<br />\n<br />\n乾粉型：射程有五至六米；適合撲滅大部分火警。<br />\n<br />\n二氧化碳型：射程有一至兩米遠；適合撲滅由油類或者警。<br />\n<br />\n滅火筒滅火嘅基本原理係向火源噴出物質，將火包圍，隔絕氧氣，令火窒息而死。你可以按照你蝸居嘅情況，買一個啱使嘅滅火筒返屋企，以便不時之需。<br />\n<br />\n不過，你一定要向合資格嘅供應商購買，因為根據《消防(裝置及設備)規例》，所有手提滅火器必須獲得消防處認可，先至可以喺香港銷售。<br />\n<br />\n另外，你亦都可以買返張滅火氈放喺廚房，一旦炒菜時鑊氣太勁而引起油火，用來撲熄啲火，唔畀火燒著其他地方，引起火災。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2egz9lcgl7v72.cloudfront.net/CMS_images/NewsImageBig/2018-05-18-14-46-38yQc72ywB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2egz9lcgl7v72.cloudfront.net%2FCMS_images%2FNewsImageBig%2F2018-05-18-14-46-38yQc72ywB.jpg&h=821a4b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蝸居達人邵存希<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/special/topics/32/article/424064/cat/126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fspecial%2Ftopics%2F32%2Farticle%2F424064%2Fcat%2F126&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=f1085d92\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/special/topics/32/article/424064/cat/126</a>"},{"pid":"01c8eb294bea7dc25a2f41fb7f389b8e2f4e677a","tid":1333853,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"水劑型：射程有六米遠；適合撲滅由紙張、布塊、木材、塑膠、雜物等引起嘅火警。<br />\n<br />\n泡劑型：射程有四至六米；除咗適合撲滅上述嘅普通火種外，亦啱撲熄由火水、電油、酒精等嘅易燃液體或者油類引起嘅火警。<br />\n<br />\n乾粉型：射程有五至六米；適合撲滅大部分火警。<br />\n<br />\n二氧化碳型：射程有一至兩米遠；適合撲滅由油類或者警。"},{"pid":"3afd91097d1aefbc053d665d65b73babe360dd00","tid":1333853,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qt6g2N7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqt6g2N7.png&h=52ab384c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.care-is.com/upload/wysiwyg/Loss_Prevention1/triangle-du-feu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.care-is.com%2Fupload%2Fwysiwyg%2FLoss_Prevention1%2Ftriangle-du-feu.gif&h=df13b63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「火三角」闡明了一場火的燃燒之規律，只有齊備以下三種元素：引火源、可燃物及助燃劑（多數情況下為氧氣），一場火方能成功燃燒，缺一不可。因此只要把任何一種元素移除，這場火就能成功撲滅。在自然環境中，如果上述三種元素的比例恰當，便可產生一場火災。"},{"pid":"0c20808fcb38eb2ebf7e2c3d5fcc6199a2894e4a","tid":1333853,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"呢隊消防隊係以火滅火喎"},{"pid":"8022a9b10098cd6b12435e1bae487dde8dfee7bf","tid":1333853,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYjFK9E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYjFK9E.png&h=29521767&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51f35f1d0b0e49bf2ad09e31745d66d7575469c8","tid":1333853,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"滅火筒用得幾秒，又難帶"},{"pid":"8efa092b0c3974c9b14941fc099ba999d0eacb46","tid":1333853,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkfirestation.com/pages/%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E6%88%91%E5%80%91.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkfirestation.com%2Fpages%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591.html&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=6da4bc54\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkfirestation.com/pages/%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E6%88%91%E5%80%91.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電話: 3464 3987<br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp.jpgwhatsapp報價查詢：96309976 <br />\n<br />\nFacebook：Firestation （滅火站） <br />\n<br />\n電郵: hongkongfirestation@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n地址:葵涌石建街17-23號建興工業大廈7/F A1室<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hzy3HXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhzy3HXQ.png&h=c20cf661&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd46557636f9dfe5476114107c4d4ffcb9616e79","tid":1333853,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51f35f1d0b0e49bf2ad09e31745d66d7575469c8","tid":1333853,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"滅火筒用得幾秒，又難帶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:06:32.000Z","msg":"一起火就可以用 同埋射程五到六米"},{"pid":"42c766435a478458ce64fdc4a047ef4f56c0d534","tid":1333853,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://stanleyc.easy-eshop.com/product_images/uploaded_images/img-3925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstanleyc.easy-eshop.com%2Fproduct_images%2Fuploaded_images%2Fimg-3925.jpg&h=a9834fb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e21c6e29876e0ea57ea98b00efb2147ac35be22","tid":1333853,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"呢個size好似唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.c